data.value: SELECT chck.ch_id ChecklistId ,chck.ch_title ChecklistTitle FROM [dbo].[rc_projects] prj INNER JOIN [dbo].[rc_rtm_active] act ON prj.pro_ID = act.act_projectID INNER JOIN [dbo].[rc_rtm_checklists] chck on act.act_checklist = chck.ch_id WHERE prj.pro_ID = @ProjectID AND chck.ch_id = 'F63339F8-D3B1-4566-9D25-7F1F9F504483' AND chck.ch_deleted = 0 AND act.act_isacctive =1
